New Delhi, the 22nd April, 2009
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 29th March, 2009:-
Dr. Anbumani Ramdoss relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of Health & Family Welfare;
(i)
(ii)
Shri R. Velu relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in
the Ministry of Railways;
Smt. Panabaka Lakshmi relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of State in the Ministry of Health & Family Welfare and assumed
the charge of the office of the Minister of State (Independent Charge) of
the Ministry of Health & Family Welfare.
(ii)
